column1: # Configuration pin/part database for PLD support.
#  Values curated from Application Note AN414
#  STATUS_pins          - instruction STATUS allows internal status 'pins' to be read much like a boundary
#                         scan chain. Three bits present used per emulated pin
#  CONF_DONE_pinpos     - which pin (measured from the end!) contains the CONF_DONE pin signal

column2: IDCODE alone is not sufficient to identify Family/Part
